00:45:27,734 --> 00:45:31,696
"Acts 3:3, Revelations 18:7,

564
00:45:32,614 --> 00:45:36,117
"Jonah 6:8, John 6:22,

565
00:45:36,743 --> 00:45:38,452
"Luke 1:7."

566
00:45:38,954 --> 00:45:40,204
