589
00:46:42,435 --> 00:46:43,810
He gave them a recipe
for potato chip dip.

590
00:46:43,895 --> 00:46:44,978
JACK: Wonderful.

591
00:46:46,314 --> 00:46:49,691
The Tooth Fairy would have
named a book he knew
Lecktor has access to.

592
00:46:49,776 --> 00:46:51,485
He'd know it from articles
he'd read about Lecktor.

593
00:46:51,569 --> 00:46:53,028
JACK: Willingham,
when he tossed his cell,

594
00:46:53,112 --> 00:46:54,988
took Polaroids so they can
get everything back in place.

595
00:46:55,072 --> 00:46:57,699
Have him meet me
with pictures
